_normalizeDecimals(address,uint256)
ENTRY_POINT

ENTRY_POINT
_normalizeDecimals(address,uint256)
ENTRY_POINT
NEW VARIABLE _decimals = uint256(ExtendedIERC20(_token).decimals())
EXPRESSION _amount = _amount.mul(10 ** (18 - _decimals))
RETURN _amount

ENTRY_POINT
_normalizeDecimals(address,uint256)
ENTRY_POINT
NEW VARIABLE _decimals = uint256(ExtendedIERC20(_token).decimals())
EXPRESSION _amount = _amount.mul(10 ** (18 - _decimals))
RETURN _amount

_normalizeDecimals(address,uint256)
ENTRY_POINT

_normalizeDecimals(address,uint256)

_normalizeDecimals(address,uint256)
ENTRY_POINT

_normalizeDecimals(address,uint256)

ENTRY_POINT
balanceOfThis()
ENTRY_POINT
NEW VARIABLE _tokens = manager.getTokens(address(this))
EXPRESSION _balance = 0
NEW VARIABLE i
BEGIN_LOOP
IF_LOOP i < _tokens.length
NEW VARIABLE _token = _tokens[i]
END_LOOP
EXPRESSION _balance = _balance.add(_normalizeDecimals(_token,IERC20(_token).balanceOf(address(this))))
RETURN _balance
EXPRESSION i ++
IF_LOOP i < _tokens.length
